PARLIAMENT - President Cyril Ramaphosa lost his cool with DA chief whip John Steenhuisen during a question and answer session in Parliament on Tuesday afternoon. The president told Steenhuisen to shut up and listen. WATCH: President Ramaphosa does the 'Ramajive' "And shut up you Steenhuisen and listen, I want you to shut up, I really want you to shut up. Steenhuisen continues to make noise," he said. This was the president's second question and answer session after he was elected president. eNCA